        <abstract> 
<p>Has received copy of CL’s <hi rend="italic">Principles</hi> [7th ed.].</p>  
<p>Comments on reading <hi rend="italic">Annales des sciences naturelles</hi>.</p> 
            <p>David Milne’s and Robert Chambers’ views on Glen Roy.</p> 
<p>Mentions sales of <hi rend="italic">South America</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Describes visit to his father at Shrewsbury.</p>
